Installation
=================
To install the "Sitemap" extension follow these simple steps:

 1. Upload the extension using the Administration panel
 2. Install the "Sitemap" extension
 3. Assign the "Sitemap" module to the page where you want the sitemap to appear 

Introduction 
=================
Sitemap displays all pages within your website.

Changelog
=================
1.4: 
    - Initial release for Bigace 3
    - Added flag to display content above sitemap
